{
  "id": "adv_card_chs_03_02",
  "title": "白石千紗 2話 諦めたくないんです",
  "script": [
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_lesson-01-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "stage01",
      "startTime": null
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "chs",
      "speakerName": "白石千紗",
      "speakerNameEn": "Chisa",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-chisa.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_chs_03_02/sud_vo_adv_card_chs_03_02-chs001.m4a",
      "text": "1、2、3、4……1、2、3、4……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "1‚ 2‚ 3‚ 4… 1‚ 2‚ 3‚ 4…",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 0.8,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_chs_03_02/sud_vo_adv_card_chs_03_02-koh001.m4a",
      "text": "うーん……やる気は伝わってくるが……\nやはり急なパート変更ですぐにうまくはいかないか",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Hmm… I can sense your motivation‚ but…\nIt's still a sudden part change‚ so it might not go well immediately.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 11.5666666667,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "chs",
      "speakerName": "白石千紗",
      "speakerNameEn": "Chisa",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-chisa.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_chs_03_02/sud_vo_adv_card_chs_03_02-chs002.m4a",
      "text": "1、2、3、4……きゃっ！",
      "translations": {
        "en": "1‚ 2‚ 3‚ 4… Ah!",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 15.5333333333,
      "sfxList": [
        {
          "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBgm/sud_se_adv_down-01.m4a",
          "delay": 4100.000000000002,
          "startTime": 19.6333333333
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_chs_03_02/sud_vo_adv_card_chs_03_02-koh002.m4a",
      "text": "大丈夫か！？\n今日は朝から踊りっぱなしだろ、少し休憩した方がいい",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Are you okay!?\nYou've been dancing since morning today‚ so you should take a short break.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 22.4,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "chs",
      "speakerName": "白石千紗",
      "speakerNameEn": "Chisa",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-chisa.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_chs_03_02/sud_vo_adv_card_chs_03_02-chs003.m4a",
      "text": "はぁはぁ……でも、ライブまで時間がありませんから\n早く踊れるようにならないと……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "*panting* But we don't have much time until the live…\nI need to be able to dance it quickly…",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 32.9,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_chs_03_02/sud_vo_adv_card_chs_03_02-koh003.m4a",
      "text": "気持ちは分かるが無理はするな\nなんならコーチにお願いして難易度を下げても……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "I understand your feelings‚ but don't push yourself too hard.\nIf you want‚ I can ask the coach to lower the difficulty…",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 38.3433333333,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "chs",
      "speakerName": "白石千紗",
      "speakerNameEn": "Chisa",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-chisa.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_chs_03_02/sud_vo_adv_card_chs_03_02-chs004.m4a",
      "text": "難易度は下げたくありません\nお願いします、このままの振り付けでやらせて下さい",
      "translations": {
        "en": "I don't want to lower the difficulty.\nPlease‚ let me continue with this choreography as it is.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 44.7333333333,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "chs",
      "speakerName": "白石千紗",
      "speakerNameEn": "Chisa",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-chisa.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_chs_03_02/sud_vo_adv_card_chs_03_02-chs005.m4a",
      "text": "週末までにはきっと……\nいえ、必ず、踊れるようになってみせますから",
      "translations": {
        "en": "I will try…\nno‚ I will surely be able to dance it by the weekend.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 51.3433333333,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_chs_03_02/sud_vo_adv_card_chs_03_02-koh004.m4a",
      "text": "……分かった\nだが無理は禁物だ。いいな？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "…I understand.\nBut overdoing it is not advisable. Got it?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 58.2,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": null,
      "speakerName": "",
      "speakerNameEn": "",
      "iconUrl": null,
      "voiceUrl": null,
      "text": "――千紗、別件の仕事中",
      "translations": {
        "en": "――Chisa‚ working on another matter.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 63.0666666667,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_photostudio-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "stage02",
      "startTime": 63.7666666667
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_photostudio-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "stage02",
      "startTime": 63.7666666667
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "chs",
      "speakerName": "白石千紗",
      "speakerNameEn": "Chisa",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-chisa.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_chs_03_02/sud_vo_adv_card_chs_03_02-chs006.m4a",
      "text": "1、2、3、4……ここでターンして……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "1‚ 2‚ 3‚ 4… And here‚ I turn…",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 65.3666666667,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_chs_03_02/sud_vo_adv_card_chs_03_02-koh005.m4a",
      "text": "千紗、もうすぐグラビアの撮影が始まるけど……\n何を観てるんだ？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Chisa‚ the gravure shoot is about to start soon…\nWhat are you looking at?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 76.7666666667,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_photostudio-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "stage02",
      "startTime": 79.4
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "chs",
      "speakerName": "白石千紗",
      "speakerNameEn": "Chisa",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-chisa.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_chs_03_02/sud_vo_adv_card_chs_03_02-chs007.m4a",
      "text": "自分のダンスを撮影した動画です\nどうしてもうまく踊れないところがあって……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "A video of myself dancing that I recorded.\nThere are some parts I just can't seem to dance well…",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 82.5666666667,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "chs",
      "speakerName": "白石千紗",
      "speakerNameEn": "Chisa",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-chisa.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_chs_03_02/sud_vo_adv_card_chs_03_02-chs008.m4a",
      "text": "動画で動きを確認してるんですけど\n観れば観るほど自分の下手さが目についちゃって……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "So I'm checking my movements in the video.\nThe more I watch it‚ the more I notice my own clumsiness…",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 89,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_photostudio-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "stage02",
      "startTime": 94.0666666667
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "chs",
      "speakerName": "白石千紗",
      "speakerNameEn": "Chisa",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-chisa.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_chs_03_02/sud_vo_adv_card_chs_03_02-chs009.m4a",
      "text": "こんなことじゃダメですよね……\nもっと努力しないと……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "This won't do‚ right…?\nI need to make more effort…",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 97.3333333333,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_photostudio-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "stage02",
      "startTime": 99.8
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_chs_03_02/sud_vo_adv_card_chs_03_02-koh006.m4a",
      "text": "仕事の合間にイメージトレーニングか……\n千紗もいろいろと工夫してるんだな",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Doing image training in between work‚ huh…\nChisa‚ you're really working hard.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 103.2666666667,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_chs_03_02/sud_vo_adv_card_chs_03_02-koh007.m4a",
      "text": "（この頑張りに応えてやりたいが）\n（俺に何か出来ることは……）",
      "translations": {
        "en": "(I want to respond to her hard work.)\n(What can I do for her…)",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 109.2,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": null,
      "speakerName": "",
      "speakerNameEn": "",
      "iconUrl": null,
      "voiceUrl": null,
      "text": "――数日後",
      "translations": {
        "en": "――A few days later",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 112.4,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_lesson-02-evening.webp",
      "bgName": "stage03",
      "startTime": 112.6666666667
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "chs",
      "speakerName": "白石千紗",
      "speakerNameEn": "Chisa",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-chisa.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_chs_03_02/sud_vo_adv_card_chs_03_02-chs010.m4a",
      "text": "はぁはぁ……\nダメ……どうしても同じところでミスしちゃう……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Haahaa… I can't do it…\nI keep making the same mistake…",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 117.1,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_chs_03_02/sud_vo_adv_card_chs_03_02-koh008.m4a",
      "text": "……千紗。ここ数日レッスンを見てきたが\nこのまま同じことをしていても上達は難しいと思う",
      "translations": {
        "en": "…Chisa‚ I've been observing your rehearsals for the past few days…\nI think it's difficult to improve if you continue doing the same thing.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 125.1666666667,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_chs_03_02/sud_vo_adv_card_chs_03_02-koh009.m4a",
      "text": "酷なことを言うようだが、間に合わせるにはやはり\n振り付けの難易度を下げるしかないんじゃないか？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "I hate to say it‚ but maybe we need to lower\nthe difficulty of the choreography to make it work.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 132.9333333333,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "chs",
      "speakerName": "白石千紗",
      "speakerNameEn": "Chisa",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-chisa.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_chs_03_02/sud_vo_adv_card_chs_03_02-chs011.m4a",
      "text": "それは……嫌です\nお願いします、このままやらせて下さい",
      "translations": {
        "en": "That… I don't want to do that.\nPlease‚ let me continue like this.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 139.1,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_chs_03_02/sud_vo_adv_card_chs_03_02-koh010.m4a",
      "text": "どうしてそこまで頑ななんだ？　難易度を下げても\nこれだけ頑張った千紗を誰も責めたりしないさ",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Why are you so stubborn? Even if we lower the difficulty…\nNo one will blame you after all the effort you've put in‚ Chisa.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 146.8333333333,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "chs",
      "speakerName": "白石千紗",
      "speakerNameEn": "Chisa",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-chisa.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_chs_03_02/sud_vo_adv_card_chs_03_02-chs012.m4a",
      "text": "そうですね……\nみんな優しいから私を責めないと思います……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "That's true…\nEveryone is kind‚ and I don't think they will blame me…",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 152.0666666667,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "chs",
      "speakerName": "白石千紗",
      "speakerNameEn": "Chisa",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-chisa.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_chs_03_02/sud_vo_adv_card_chs_03_02-chs013.m4a",
      "text": "でも、私が嫌なんです……諦めたくないんです",
      "translations": {
        "en": "But I don't want that… I don't want to give up.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 156.5,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "chs",
      "speakerName": "白石千紗",
      "speakerNameEn": "Chisa",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-chisa.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_chs_03_02/sud_vo_adv_card_chs_03_02-chs014.m4a",
      "text": "私が怜ちゃんのかわりに踊るって決めた後\n寮に戻ってサニピのみんなと話したんです",
      "translations": {
        "en": "After I decided to dance in place of Rei-chan‚\nI went back to the dorm and talked to everyone in Sunny Peace.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 165.8333333333,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "chs",
      "speakerName": "白石千紗",
      "speakerNameEn": "Chisa",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-chisa.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_chs_03_02/sud_vo_adv_card_chs_03_02-chs015.m4a",
      "text": "ソロパートをやりたいって言い出したのは私だから\n私の口からちゃんと説明しなきゃと思って……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "It was me who brought up wanting to do the solo part.\nI felt like I needed to explain properly in my own words…",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 173.7,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "chs",
      "speakerName": "白石千紗",
      "speakerNameEn": "Chisa",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-chisa.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_chs_03_02/sud_vo_adv_card_chs_03_02-chs016.m4a",
      "text": "星見市にいた頃は目の前のことで精一杯だったけど\n東京に出て、いろんなお仕事をするようになって……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "When I was in Hoshimi City‚ I was only focused on what was right in front of me‚\nBut since coming to Tokyo and doing various jobs…",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 183.6,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "chs",
      "speakerName": "白石千紗",
      "speakerNameEn": "Chisa",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-chisa.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_chs_03_02/sud_vo_adv_card_chs_03_02-chs017.m4a",
      "text": "少しだけ視野が広がって……私が頑張れば\nもっといろんな景色が見られるんだって分かって……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "My perspective has expanded a bit… I realized that if I work hard‚\nI'll be able to see more different sceneries…",
        "id": ""
      },
