    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "chs",
      "speakerName": "白石千紗",
      "speakerNameEn": "Chisa",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-chisa.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_chs_03_02/sud_vo_adv_card_chs_03_02-chs018.m4a",
      "text": "もっと挑戦したい……もっと成長したい……\nそう思えるようになったから……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "I want to challenge myself more… I want to grow more…\nBecause that's how it seems to me. ……",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 200.6,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "chs",
      "speakerName": "白石千紗",
      "speakerNameEn": "Chisa",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-chisa.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_chs_03_02/sud_vo_adv_card_chs_03_02-chs019.m4a",
      "text": "だから、今度のソロパートは私に挑戦させてほしいって\nみんなにお願いしたんです",
      "translations": {
        "en": "That's why I want to take on this solo part…\nI asked everyone for their support.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 208.3333333333,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_chs_03_02/sud_vo_adv_card_chs_03_02-koh011.m4a",
      "text": "内気な千紗が自分から挑戦したいと言い出すなんて\nみんな驚いたんじゃないか？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "It's surprising for the shy Chisa to come forward and say so.\nI bet everyone was amazed‚ right?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 214.6666666667,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "chs",
      "speakerName": "白石千紗",
      "speakerNameEn": "Chisa",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-chisa.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_chs_03_02/sud_vo_adv_card_chs_03_02-chs020.m4a",
      "text": "はい……でも、みんなすぐに賛成してくれました\nそうしようって言ってくれて……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Yes… but everyone immediately agreed.\nThey said let's do it…",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 221.9333333333,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "chs",
      "speakerName": "白石千紗",
      "speakerNameEn": "Chisa",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-chisa.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_chs_03_02/sud_vo_adv_card_chs_03_02-chs021.m4a",
      "text": "さくらちゃんは、ひたむきに努力してきた\n千紗ちゃんなら絶対出来るよって言ってくれて……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Sakura-chan said\n\"Chisa-chan can definitely do it‚ you've been working diligently…\"",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 227.8333333333,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "chs",
      "speakerName": "白石千紗",
      "speakerNameEn": "Chisa",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-chisa.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_chs_03_02/sud_vo_adv_card_chs_03_02-chs022.m4a",
      "text": "雫ちゃんは、私がソロパートを\nかっこよく踊る姿を見たいって言ってくれて……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Shizuku-chan said\nshe wants to see me dance the solo part coolly…",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 235.0333333333,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "chs",
      "speakerName": "白石千紗",
      "speakerNameEn": "Chisa",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-chisa.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_chs_03_02/sud_vo_adv_card_chs_03_02-chs023.m4a",
      "text": "遙子さんは、私達がサポートするから\n安心して踊っていいんだよって……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Haruko-san said \"we'll support you‚\nso you can dance without worries…\"",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 243.0333333333,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "chs",
      "speakerName": "白石千紗",
      "speakerNameEn": "Chisa",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-chisa.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_chs_03_02/sud_vo_adv_card_chs_03_02-chs024.m4a",
      "text": "それに怜ちゃんは……「最近の千紗が熱心にダンスに\n取り組んでいたのを、ずっとそばで見てたから……」",
      "translations": {
        "en": "And Rei-chan said‚\n\"I've been watching Chisa's dedication to dance lately…\"",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 250.8333333333,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "chs",
      "speakerName": "白石千紗",
      "speakerNameEn": "Chisa",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-chisa.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_chs_03_02/sud_vo_adv_card_chs_03_02-chs025.m4a",
      "text": "「今の千紗なら安心して任せられる。ソロパートを\n私は千紗に踊ってほしい」って言ってくれて……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "\"I can trust Chisa now.\"\n\"I want Chisa to dance the solo part\"",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 259.9666666667,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_chs_03_02/sud_vo_adv_card_chs_03_02-koh012.m4a",
      "text": "千紗が地道に努力していたことを\nみんなちゃんと見ていてくれたんだな",
